Ecobank Seeks ‘Significant Equity Stake’ in Ghanaian Lender Trust Bank

-- B y   M o s e s   M o z a r t   D z a w u
-- 
2011-07-18T15:11:14Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-18/ecobank-seeks-significant-equity-stake-in-ghanaian-lender-trust-bank.html
Ecobank Transnational Inc. (ETI) , a
Togolese lender that operates in 32 African countries, wants to
acquire a “significant equity stake” in state-owned Ghanaian
lender The Trust Bank Ltd.  The deal would combine Trust Bank’s operations with
Ecobank’s unit in  Ghana , the lender said in a statement e-mailed
by the Ghana Stock Exchange today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Moses Mozart Dzawu in Accra at 
 mdzawu@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Emily Bowers at 
 ebowers1@bloomberg.net  